ros2_wheelbot controleaza un AMR omnidirectional care are virtual 4 wheel joint si 4 steering joint la 4 colturi controlate prin  topic_based_ros2_control  si real 2 module diferential-drive (vezi www.wheelbot.tech) 
jointstate_aggregator_2.cpp - centralizeaza starea jointurilor 
jointstate_to_twist_2.cpp transforma comenzile jointsate in twist  
analizeaza fisierul mcap atasat , verifica corelatia dintre topicurile  /amr_joint_commands - /amr_joint_states  -  /FR_amr_joint_states -  /FR_drive_joint_commands - /FR_drive_joint_states , amr_joint_comands
swerve_drive_controller pune initial steering joints la zero deci modulul FR ar trebui sa se duca la zero dar nu reuseste,

lantul de comenzi :
swerve_controller → /amr_joint_commands 
    → jointstate_to_twist_4 → /FR_drive_controller/cmd_vel
        → diff_drive_controller → /FR_drive_joint_commands
            → topic_based_ros2_control → (Zenoh) → FR_picoros_node (ESP32)